album.title: Lady Killers II (Christoph Andersson Remix) - Single

wiki.summary: “Lady Killers II (Christoph Andersson Remix)” is a song by Oakland rapper G-Eazy and his long-time producer Christoph Andersson. The track was first released on SoundCloud on November 14, 2013, and remixes the 2011 track, “Lady Killers“ with Hoodie Allen. The song later appeared on the remix EP, Must Be Twice. In early 2024, the song began to trend on TikTok and was soon officially released on streaming platforms after a decade. Read more on Last.fm.
